{"title":"雨后","date":"2020-10-25T15:13:05.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 25, 2020","L":"10/25/2020","MM-DD":"10-25"},"thumbnail":"https://cdn.wardzhou.art/img/birds-4389024_640.webp","link":"2020/10/25/AfterRain","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-12-14T15:10:11.492Z","content":"<p>你让我重新记起<br>\n本不属于这个季节的事物<br>\n消融的河水<br>\n四月的淡樱<br>\n清冽而香甜的<br>\n焦糖、布丁、薄荷<br>\n还有早春时<br>\n不愿放下的火炉</p>\n<p>田野里<br>\n热潮伴着冷霜<br>\n翩然起舞<br>\n雨打醒了梦中的人<br>\n盛夏未至<br>\n只迎寒冬</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Cover image by <a href=\"https://pixabay.com/photos/birds-sparrow-rain-animals-nature-4389024/\" target=\"_blank\">Alexey_Marcov</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n","prev":{"title":"平流层的汪洋","link":"2020/11/29/OceanicStratosphere"},"next":{"title":"Eve","link":"2020/10/14/Eve"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2020/10/25/AfterRain/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Birch","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International(<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","updated":"December 14, 2020"},"reading_time":"85 words in 1 min"}